v-model="newTask" ... going to watch newTask in state
v-model="task.done"... watching done attr in state

events
@keyup.enter="addTask($event)" - whenever user hits enter key,
- call up method addTask, which will add the value of input to state 

@click="check(task)" - change state to true

how to bind class? :class="{'is-done': task.done}
-if task.done is true, apply the class